snippet.textDisplay:
Really, this song shocked me. I'm not a number one fan, and I don't actually know about all the references that you puted on it. But I could completly understand how hard you fought in you whole life. Even if I don't get everything about your career and personal life, I know the most important and hard events of your life as a famous. So, knowing that, I can say that you are a such strong women, and a model for youth. I'm sure you can teach to the world a better path. Trough your music and specially this song, everybody can know about your mistakes; so I think is so brave to show your waeknesses, but giving the message that it's okay to have them. U can be proud of yourself, bc even if made mistakes, u worked so hard to end those situations. And now, u became a better person for yourself. You have realized that you are THE first and most important love of your life.

Love ya 💕💓💜
